## Limitations

The report is based on available online resources and may not encompass all perspectives or the most recent data on the topic. The lack of specific publication dates for some sources may affect the timeliness of the information. Additionally, the focus was primarily on economic and social factors, potentially overlooking environmental or political influences on migration to megacities.

